<p>I feel bad for downvoting, since it's not a bad piece of writing. But I'm of the opinion that anything that further elucidates on 055 necessarily detracts from it. I don't know if the concept in this story would work as a separate SCP without being too close to 055, but the hook is different. SCP-055 very nicely grabs the reader's curiosity and produces a feeling of dread; this guy inspires pity and also a different sort of dread (&quot;wow, it would suck to be that guy&quot;).</p>
<p>Tricky subject material.</p>

							</div>

								
					
